{"tid":1635883,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發 勇武快閃嘅初心忘記曬！快啲入嚟睇！","createTime":"2019-10-07T15:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:16:28.000Z","uid":167548,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4592849d9ea596ab1cdff00210fc4f4b92b45d69","tid":1635883,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"堵路 裝修 所有野都是增加管治成本！<br />\n前者癱瘓交通, 達至連鎖反應, 影響所有持份者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是我屌你老母自從緊急法之後, 夜晚街上面人都唔多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />車都沒幾架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堵路有咩撚用啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界無論是閒日定假期統一日頭繁忙時段堵佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10.4 政府製造宵禁情緒, 夜晚出動, 街上面人都唔多個, 有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界返屋企不被捕, 轉方向, 聽日返工放工時段開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全港三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"61093eb5e041be60e89133ea56bc849363db1b6f","tid":1635883,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"夜晚出嚟快閃, 除左被狗拉之外個效益是好唔化算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee6b6821e6e91bfbef1d120ea677c24c3f35ffb","tid":1635883,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"現時晚上街上面大多是自已友, 根本搞撚到班藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e44ece152ddb4ac82776b19e97755f499b4e0a6","tid":1635883,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:37:44.000Z","msg":"車都唔見有幾多架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;佢出左宵禁堵嚟有閪樣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽朝起身各區快閃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1155951c8e5b2d8f63349c4b4676ba184be035a2","tid":1635883,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"罷你老母<br />\n前日吹完集中港島累死晒手足<br />\n今日又吹三罷累人"},{"pid":"483c677f93cdacc6bdc49a1bb364c177b53d6092","tid":1635883,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"屋企要人啊！<br />\n重整戰略，出左緊急法個宵禁令你出街快閃嘅效益是接近零啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;"},{"pid":"911d454dd193836a9f5dcdc64527d502519fd918","tid":1635883,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1155951c8e5b2d8f63349c4b4676ba184be035a2","tid":1635883,"uid":143230,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"罷你老母<br />\n前日吹完集中港島累死晒手足<br />\n今日又吹三罷累人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15